m offers a robust solution to provide long-term\ninterface between an array of precisely defined microelectrodes and deep-brain\nareas of a behaving rodent. The microdrive allowed us to fine-tune the probe\nlocation and easily scan through the regions of interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Aug 2017 22:42:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-03"}
