thm for these family of codes. In this context, recall that for\ngeneral codes, efficient decoding algorithms do not exist if some widely\nbelieved complexity theoretic assumptions are true.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Aug 2017 06:36:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 10 Jun 2018 12:11:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-12"}
